WEBVTT

00:00.420 --> 00:02.830
♪♪

00:12.500 --> 00:14.460
♪ I'm seeing lots of spots ♪

00:14.460 --> 00:16.040
♪ Plenty of polka dots ♪

00:18.170 --> 00:20.120
♪ Get those puppies! ♪

00:20.120 --> 00:21.790
♪ Can't catch
a furry flurry ♪

00:21.790 --> 00:23.540
♪ Running in a blurry hurry ♪

00:26.080 --> 00:27.170
♪ Get those puppies! ♪

00:28.330 --> 00:30.620
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:30.620 --> 00:32.170
♪ Canines on the run ♪

00:32.170 --> 00:34.040
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:34.040 --> 00:35.380
♪ Them doggone dogs are fun ♪

00:35.380 --> 00:37.120
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

